        <header>
            <h1>QuoteCreator Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p class="meta">
                <strong>Effective Date:</strong> October 10, 2025<br>
                <strong>Last Updated:</strong> October 9, 2025<br>
                <strong>Version:</strong> 1.0
